---
title: Chicken Sausage & Sweet Potato Soup with Herb Butter Toast Points
description: Rain or shine, warm or cool, it’s tough not to crave a big bowl of soup (i.e. the culinary equivalent of a bear hug). Tonight’s soup is chock full of goodness — that is to say spiced chicken sausage, chunks of sweet potato, and tender curly kale. And because no good brothy bowl is complete without some bread for dunking, we’re also throwing in buttery, herby toast points. Get ready for a meal as satisfying as it is delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/606cb4a587f1e825ee231a00-6da7d9a4.jpg
